  <brief_title>Laparoscopic and Open Ventral Hernia Repair Using the Intramesh T1</brief_title>
  <official_title>Laparoscopic and Open Ventral Hernia Repair Using the Intramesh T1: a Prospective, Multicenter Registry</official_title>
  <sponsors>
