  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the registry is to evaluate safety and efficacy of the Intramesh T1. This
      registry will collect data from 100 patients treated for a ventral hernia repair.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Completed</overall_status>
